Venom (1981 - UK)

Horror / Thriller

starring . . . . Klaus Kinski, Oliver Reed, Nicol Williamson, Sterling Hayden
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0084854/


An international criminal enlists Ruth Hopkins' maid and chauffeur in a scheme to kidnap her asthmatic ten-year-old son Philip for ransom. As the plot begins to unfold, Philip has just brought home a snake from a local importer, unaware that his new pet has been accidentally switched with a deadly black mamba destined for a toxicology lab. The lab reports the mix-up, and a police officer is dispatched to the Hopkins residence, only to be shot by the panicking chauffeur.
